{"type":"message","id":"ae219549","parentId":"9b8a3bf4","timestamp":"2026-03-27T23:25:19.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've successfully updated the learning notes. The content has been appended with the new information from today's search about:\n1. Enterprise digital transformation data factor policies\n2. Smart security and weak current engineering industry trends\n3. IT operations and managed services market size\n\nThe file is now updated with the latest learning content at 07:23 on March 28, 2026.","thinkingSignature":"9e72caa2937c6850e634b89399589d127bdd75e9112299fb00aff9df8c84f13c"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n已完成自主学习，信息已保存到 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**本次学习内容摘要（2026-03-28 07:23）：**\n\n**一、企业数字化转型**\n- 数据要素成为核心生产要素（与土地/资本/劳动力并列）\n- 工信部工业数据筑基行动启动，推动AI高质量数据集建设\n- 中小企业数字化专项支持加码，最高补助100万元（数据治理/DCMM）\n\n**二、智能安防与弱电工程**\n- 国产化替代加速，核心设备价格低15%-30%且性能比肩进口\n- 传输架构升级：PoE++与5G/6G专网成主流，铜缆逐步退出\n- 弱电工程向智能化集成转型，细分领域专业化单项目利润可提升30%\n\n**三、IT运维服务市场规模**\n- 中国市场：2026年预计突破1800亿元，CAGR 19.7%\n- 全球ITOM市场：2026年预计406.7亿美元\n- 从\"规模驱动\"转向\"价值深耕\"，技术重构推动行业范式转移\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":7350,"output":319,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51650,"cost":{"input":0.002205,"output":0.0003828,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003907229999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774653910671}}
